Package org.openlca.geo

package org.openlca.geo
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    GeoJson2Kml
    A minimal converter of GeoJSON to KML (as used in openLCA).
    GeoJsonImport
    The GeoJSON import tries to identify the corresponding locations in the database via the feature attributes in a feature collection and updates the corresponding geo data of that location if a corresponding feature was found.
    Kml2GeoJson
    A minimal converter of KML to GeoJSON (as used in openLCA).
